  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Race:</strong> Dwarf&nbsp;<br /><strong>Replaced Trait(s):</strong> Stability, Stonecunning&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Dwarves with this racial trait gain a +4 racial bonus to their CMD against disarm and steal<sup>APG</sup> combat maneuvers and a +2 racial bonus on Perception checks to notice Sleight of Hand attempts. If a dwarf with this trait notices a Sleight of Hand attempt to steal from him and the dwarf is not flat-footed or has Combat Reflexes, the attempt triggers an attack of opportunity from that dwarf. This racial trait replaces stability and stonecunning.</p>",
